title: Louis Vuitton Alma Damier PM
description: Louis Vuitton Alma PM bag in Damier coated canvas. Featuring a brown cowhide leather trim, gold-toned hardware and dual rolled handles. The double zip closure opens to a red textile-lined interior with flat pockets. Approximate dimensions: 32cm(Base-L) x 24cm(H) x 16cm(D), 10cm handle drop. Accompanied by a detachable brown leather clochette, keys, padlock, Louis Vuitton receipt, dustbag and box. With Entrupy certificate of authenticity. (Pre-owned)
